title: Students voted ‘Most Likely to Succeed’ are now a mixed bag of emotions (16 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Thanks to these former classmates, we get to look back and see just how accurate the High School superlative ended up being. From the looks of things, it seems as though some people definitely lived up to their monikers, while others seemed to have crashed and burned. If you were popular enough to dawn one of the coveted yearbook superlatives, let us know how it turned out in the comments below. 2
